Jerold T. Hevener https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jerold_T._Hevener 0 Jerold T. Hevener (April 30, 1873, date of death unknown) was an American film actor and director. He appeared in 36 films and directed a further 18 between 1912 and 1917. He was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania.
